item.title: [SIMPLE] Error
item.dc:creator: @Skiire Skiire
item.description:
@Skiire wrote:

Semi-colons are used to signify the end of a statement.

[spoiler=not a statement]
if (xyz) {
[/spoiler]
[spoiler=a statement]
System.out.println(“xyz”);
[/spoiler]
